name: Pieces by R.F. Bongarten
description:
"Like peanut candy
I eat the candy of life in pieces
Because allergy exaggeration
All That's Too Much From Allergy
That's why the word pieces
can be good
not just bad
As in the phrase: "Heart in pieces".
Even because the heart regenerates
Have the pieces of peanut candy?
ha, these my friend
Go beyond the toilet"

By R.F. Bongarten, brazilian artist.
